Class TreeMap<Key,Val>

  • java.lang.Object
    • dove.util.treelib.Tree<Key>
      • dove.util.struct.tree.TreeMap<Key,Val>
  • Type Parameters:
    Key - every value can be accessed by an array of this type as key
    Val - Values saved
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Comparable<Tree<Key>>, java.lang.Iterable

    public class TreeMap<Key,Val>
extends Tree<Key>
    creates a treemap that can be used to relate every key to a value.
